          "landing_testimonial_title": "Voices of the Pakistani Community",
          "landing_testimonial_1_quote": "I fixed my neighbor's water pump, and in return, his wife taught my daughter how to embroider. Gadd Kaam made it possible. This is a blessing for our village.",
          "landing_testimonial_1_author": "Iqbal Hussain",
          "landing_testimonial_1_role": "Mechanic, Punjab",
          "landing_testimonial_2_quote": "Through the Women-Only Zone, I found a secure and private safe space to swap my baking recipes for sewing tutorials. I matched with Kanza and we both learned so much!",
          "landing_testimonial_2_author": "Samina Akhtar",
          "landing_testimonial_2_role": "Home Chef, Sindh",
          "landing_testimonial_3_quote": "I swapped my Python web scraping expertise for 8 hours of English tutoring. Gadd Kaam completely eliminates cash constraints. Pure community collaboration!",
          "landing_testimonial_3_author": "Ahmad Shah",
          "landing_testimonial_3_role": "Software Student, Islamabad",
          "landing_faq_tag": "FAQ Desk",
          "landing_faq_title": "Frequently Swapped Queries",
          "landing_faq_q1": "Is there really no cash involved?",
          "landing_faq_a1": "Yes, absolutely! Gadd Kaam operates strictly on a cashless system where you barter one hour of your talent for one hour of someone else's.",
          "landing_faq_q2": "How is safety guaranteed?",
          "landing_faq_a2": "All accounts require CNIC verification, profile vetting, and secure remote escrow confirmations to protect both swappers.",
          "landing_faq_q3": "Can I swap remote services?",
          "landing_faq_a3": "Yes! Gadd Kaam supports both in-person local swaps and completely digital/remote swaps (like graphic design or coding).",
          "landing_faq_q4": "What is the Women-Only Zone?",
          "landing_faq_a4": "A secure, verified private safe space exclusively visible to female swappers to practice safe and comfortable barter.",
