          "landing_journey_title": "Ready to Begin Your Skill Journey?",
          "landing_journey_desc": "Proceed directly to the main Homepage, discover matching profiles, and decide to Log In or Sign Up inside our premium talent swap dashboard.",
          "landing_journey_btn": "Go to Homepage",
          "about_title": "About Gadd Kaam",
          "about_subtitle": "Empowering communities by connecting skills cash-free across Pakistan.",
          "about_mission_title": "Our Mission",
          "about_mission_desc": "Gadd Kaam (which translates to 'Assemble/Match Work') was founded to break financial barriers. We believe that money should never be a constraint for self-improvement, learning, and growth. Our platform enables community members to trade their talents hour-for-hour without cash.",
          "about_fyp_title": "Final Year Project Ethos",
          "about_fyp_desc": "Developed as a premier Final Year Project (FYP), Gadd Kaam stands as a testament to engineering a secure, fully-vetted, non-monetized barter system. We employ custom matching models, CNIC validation procedures, and double-confirmation state engines.",
          "about_why_title": "Why 'Gadd Kaam'?",
          "about_why_desc": "In times of inflation, cashless barter provides a reliable alternative. We aim to revive the ancestral tradition of trading service-for-service, scaled with modern security protocols, gender-safe spaces, and province-specific hubs.",
          "contact_title": "Contact Us",
          "contact_subtitle": "Have questions or need assistance? Reach out to our dedicated support hub.",
          "contact_get_in_touch": "Get In Touch",
          "contact_desc": "Fill out the contact form below or reach us directly via our verified email and telephone coordinates. Our dispute resolution and validation desk is active 24/7.",
          "contact_email_lbl": "Support Email",
          "contact_address_lbl": "Headquarters Address",
          "contact_address_val": "Gadd Kaam FYP Suite, Sector H-9, Islamabad, Pakistan",
          "contact_phone_lbl": "Direct Hotline",
          "contact_name_lbl": "Your Full Name",
          "contact_name_ph": "Enter your full name...",
          "contact_email_ph": "Enter your email address...",
          "contact_msg_lbl": "Your Message",
          "contact_msg_ph": "Describe your query or dispute details...",
          "contact_send_btn": "Send Message",
          "faq_title_page": "Gadd Kaam FAQ Hub",
          "faq_subtitle": "Common answers regarding zero-cash swaps, escrow protection, and verification.",
          "faq_q1": "How does the cashless hour-for-hour swap work?",
          "faq_a1": "It's simple. You list a skill (e.g. Web Development) and search for another (e.g. AC Repair). When you matched, you agree to swap work. 1 hour of your software coding is valued exactly the same as 1 hour of their hardware fix.",
          "faq_q2": "What keeps Gadd Kaam safe and secure?",
          "faq_a2": "We require CNIC documentation, profile vetting, and secure double-confirmation escrow states. Both users must explicitly click 'Confirm Skill Received' for the swap to settle successfully.",
          "faq_q3": "Is there any commission or subscription fee?",
          "faq_a3": "Never. Gadd Kaam is a strictly cash-free platform. There are no fees, no subscriptions, and no money involved. It is built entirely for community uplift.",
          "faq_q4": "How do I earn badges on my profile?",
          "faq_a4": "Badges are awarded automatically for swapping milestones (e.g. 'First Swap') or manually by platform admins to reward exemplary community contribution.",
          "dispute_title": "Dispute Resolution Hub",
          "dispute_subtitle": "Fair play, clear guidelines, and zero-cash mediation policies.",
          "dispute_how_title": "How Disputes are Resolved",
          "dispute_how_desc": "Since Gadd Kaam is a cashless exchange, disputes usually involve incomplete work or quality discrepancies. Our admin mediation panel steps in with a transparent three-step resolution process.",
          "dispute_s1_title": "1. Mediation File",
          "dispute_s1_desc": "If a swapper fails to fulfill their hourly barter, you can open a dispute from your dashboard. This freezes the active swap state and alerts our administration team.",
          "dispute_s2_title": "2. Evidence Review",
          "dispute_s2_desc": "Admins review chat history logs, request photos, or call both parties to understand the scope of the disagreement neutrally.",
          "dispute_s3_title": "3. Resolution Action",
          "dispute_s3_l1": "Refund of held barter hours to the victim's account.",
          "dispute_s3_l2": "Temporary suspension of the offending user's profile.",
          "dispute_s3_l3": "Permanent ban for repeat policy violations or cash solicitation.",
          "dispute_note_title": "Barter Guidelines Note",
          "dispute_note_desc": "We encourage clear conversation before starting work. Always outline specific expectations, dates, and locations beforehand to avoid disputes.",
          "privacy_title": "Privacy & Data Policy",
          "privacy_updated": "Last updated: May 23, 2026",
          "privacy_intro_title": "Your Privacy is Secure",
          "privacy_intro_desc": "Gadd Kaam values your trust. We do not sell your personal data. All CNIC uploads, telephone coordinates, and profile details are encrypted securely in our servers.",
          "privacy_collect_title": "Information We Collect",
          "privacy_collect_l1": "CNIC images for profile validation (immediately encrypted, never shared).",
          "privacy_collect_l2": "Contact details (Name, Email, Verified Phone).",
          "privacy_collect_l3": "Marketplace skill offers and request logs.",
          "privacy_collect_l4": "Real-time chat history logs for dispute resolution.",
          "privacy_use_title": "How We Use Your Data",
          "privacy_use_desc": "We use your information exclusively to run the cashless marketplace safely, resolve dispute files, and block fraudulent profiles.",
          "privacy_use_l1": "Vetting identities of active swappers.",
          "privacy_use_l2": "Mediating dispute files and chat analysis.",
          "privacy_use_l3": "Sending matching skill recommendations.",
          "privacy_use_l4": "Powering the verified badge awarding system.",
          "privacy_sec_title": "High Security Standards",
          "privacy_sec_desc": "Our servers use AES-256 data protection. CNIC verification is conducted by designated admins with strict access controls. Your data remains fully protected.",
          "privacy_contact_title": "Data Protection Officer",
          "privacy_contact_desc": "For data removal requests or security inquiries, email privacy@gaddkaam.pk.",
          "terms_title": "Terms of Service",
          "terms_subtitle": "User boundaries, fyp disclaimer, and barter conduct rules.",
          "terms_s1_title": "1. Project Scope & FYP Disclaimer",
          "terms_s1_desc": "Gadd Kaam is developed as an academic Final Year Project. By registering, you acknowledge that the platform is provided 'as-is' for community testing, with no financial liabilities attached.",
          "terms_s2_title": "2. Absolute Cash Prohibition",
          "terms_s2_desc": "Gadd Kaam is strictly a cashless barter platform. Requesting, offering, or accepting rupees, cash, or virtual money is a direct violation of service. Any user soliciting money will be permanently banned.",
          "terms_s3_title": "3. User Conduct Boundaries",
          "terms_s3_desc": "Swappers must maintain professional and respectful behavior. When swapping skills, you agree to:",
          "terms_s3_l1": "Be punctual for in-person local swaps.",
          "terms_s3_l2": "Deliver competent, honest service as outlined in requests.",
          "terms_s3_l3": "Never solicit cash, products, or external payments.",
          "terms_s3_l4": "Respect the safety protocols of the Women-Only Zone.",
          "terms_s4_title": "4. Account Verification",
          "terms_s4_desc": "Users must provide authentic CNIC documents. Creating duplicate profiles or spoofing credentials is strictly prohibited and subject to immediate suspension.",
          "terms_s5_title": "5. Termination",
          "terms_s5_desc": "Gadd Kaam reserves the right to terminate accounts that violate terms, engage in harassment, or disrupt the cash-free community ethos.",
          "how_page_badge": "Interactive timeline",
          "how_page_title": "Cashless Barter Mechanics",
          "how_page_subtitle": "Discover the zero-cash hourly exchange pillars and learn how to matched successfully.",
          "how_page_ethos_title": "Zero-Money Ethos",
          "how_page_ethos_desc": "Gadd Kaam completely bypasses currency. We believe that everyone possesses valuable talent, and time is the ultimate equalizer. By swapping one hour of your service for one hour of another, we create a thriving community resilient to economic inflation.",
          "how_page_step_btn": "Step",
          "how_page_step1_title": "1. Post Your Offered Skill",
          "how_page_step1_desc": "Create a free skill card showing what you do (e.g. Software Coding, Tailoring, or AC Service) and describe what you want in return.",
          "how_page_step2_title": "2. Discover Vetted Talents",
          "how_page_step2_desc": "Browse the community marketplace. You can filter by remote/local tasks, search specific categories, or access the protected Women-Only zone.",
          "how_page_step3_title": "3. Send Swap Request",
          "how_page_step3_desc": "Submit a request to swap. Describe your project scope, location, and suggest how many hours you wish to barter.",
          "how_page_step4_title": "4. Verify Work & Earn Badges",
          "how_page_step4_desc": "Perform the hourly swap. Once completed, both swappers confirm success to release held hours and automatically build your marketplace reputation badges.",
          "how_page_conduct_title": "Our Barter Conduct Pillars",
          "how_page_conduct_s1_title": "Honest Hourly Vows",
          "how_page_conduct_s1_desc": "Trade hour-for-hour. Deliver sincere work and respect your partner's time dedication fully.",
          "how_page_conduct_s2_title": "Absolute No Cash",
          "how_page_conduct_s2_desc": "Gadd Kaam is completely free of rupees. No tips, no material additions, no cash transactions allowed.",
          "how_page_conduct_s3_title": "Identity Protection",
          "how_page_conduct_s3_desc": "Keep chats on Gadd Kaam's secure servers until trust is validated. Meet in public nodes for safety.",
          "safety_page_badge": "Safety First",
          "safety_page_title": "Trust, Safety & Security Hub",
          "safety_page_subtitle": "How we engineer a highly secure, verified, and private barter environment for our community.",
          "safety_page_report_title": "Witnessed Policy Violation? Report Instantly",
          "safety_page_report_desc": "Every single page and messaging timeline has a designated 'Report User' button. If someone demands cash, behaves unprofessionally, or violates safety, report them immediately. Our admin meditation team investigates chat history logs to enforce permanent bans.",
          "safety_page_badge_title": "Verified Performance Badges",
          "safety_page_badge_desc": "Earn badges like 'Verified Swapper' by completing CNIC validation, and 'Top Swapper' by maintaining high-quality exchanges. These badges appear prominently on your profile.",
          "safety_page_badge_btn": "Contact Support Center",
          "safety_page_tip1_title": "1. CNIC Verified Profiles",
          "safety_page_tip1_desc": "Prioritize swapping with users who carry the verified icon. You can complete your own verification by uploading CNIC front/back images securely in your settings.",
          "safety_page_tip2_title": "2. Public Meetup Nodes",
          "safety_page_tip2_desc": "If your swap is in-person (e.g. tutoring, appliance repairs), always coordinate to meet in crowded public areas like neighborhood cafes or university campuses.",
          "safety_page_tip3_title": "3. Keep Messaging Secure",
          "safety_page_tip3_desc": "Conduct all negotiations within our AES-256 encrypted chat interface. Refrain from sharing sensitive address coordinates until work begins.",
          "safety_page_tip4_title": "4. Protected Women's Zone",
          "safety_page_tip4_desc": "Female users can toggle the exclusive Women-Only zone to browse listings posted by other verified women, guaranteeing absolute privacy and safety.",
          "stories_page_success_badge": "Provincial Swaps",
          "stories_page_success_title": "Provincial Barter Success Stories",
          "stories_page_success_subtitle": "Witness how citizens across Punjab, Sindh, KPK, and Balochistan trade skills cashless.",
          "stories_page_success_stat_hours": "Barter Hours Exchanged",
          "stories_page_success_stat_swappers": "Vetted Profiles Connected",
          "stories_page_success_stat_rating": "Average Swapper Rating",
          "stories_page_success_write_title": "Begin Your Barter Journey Today",
          "stories_page_success_write_desc": "Trade your competencies inflation-free. Create your free card, match with neighbors, and earn trust badges.",
          "stories_page_success_btn_start": "Post Your Skill Now",
          "stories_page_success_btn_browse": "Browse Marketplace",
          "stories_page_success_s1_names": "Zainab & Kanza (Karachi)",
          "stories_page_success_s1_quote": "I needed a professional portfolio website to show my graphic designs. Kanza coded my complete portfolio in React, and in exchange, I designed her brand logos and social media banners. We swapped 12 hours cashless!",
          "stories_page_success_s2_names": "Bilal & Tariq (Lahore)",
          "stories_page_success_s2_quote": "My brother had a job interview but lacked confidence. Tariq matched with us online and spent 6 hours doing mock interviews. In return, I visited Tariq's house and fixed all leaking kitchen plumbing. Zero rupees spent!",
          "stories_page_success_s3_names": "Maria & Ahmad (Peshawar)",
          "stories_page_success_s3_quote": "As an online writer, I wanted to automate data compilation. Ahmad wrote a custom Python scraping script for my work, and in return, I wrote 5 SEO-optimized blogs for his website. Completed remotely and smoothly!",
          "stories_page_success_s4_names": "Ghalib & Zubair (Quetta)",
          "stories_page_success_s4_quote": "My son was struggling with university entrance algebra. Zubair tutored him for 8 hours. In return, I replaced Zubair's cracked smartphone screen and battery. A perfect talent swap with outstanding results!",

